Ewler 0.1
--------------------------------

Ewler is a ui editor and generator written with the Enlightenment Foundation Libraries (http://www.enlightenment.org).  It depends on a large number of libraries that are only available in CVS at the moment, see http://enlightenment.org/Enlightenment/Get_Enlightenment/Build_Notes.html for installation instructions of these development libraries.

To install:

./configure
make
make install

To run:

ewler [project file]

Feel free to mail werkt@users.sourceforge.net with any questions, suggestions or just to say hi.

Enjoy :)
